<section class="pg-section" data-section="The Science Behind Your Skin Transformation">
  <h2 class="pg-h">The Science Behind Your Skin Transformation</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Discover how ClearLift's advanced laser technology works beneath the surface to reveal your most radiant skin</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">What is ClearLift?</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">ClearLift is a revolutionary non-invasive laser treatment that works beneath your skin's surface to stimulate natural collagen production. Unlike traditional lasers, ClearLift requires zero downtime while delivering visible results.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Using advanced Q-switched laser technology, ClearLift sends precise bursts of energy deep into your skin layers, triggering your body's natural healing response. This process rebuilds collagen and elastin from within, giving you firmer, smoother, more youthful-looking skin.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Safe for all skin types and tones, ClearLift addresses fine lines, sun damage, uneven texture, and enlarged pores in just 30-60 minutes per session.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Laser Energy Delivery</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">Precise laser pulses penetrate deep beneath the skin surface</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Collagen Stimulation</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">Natural healing response triggers new collagen production</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Skin Renewal</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">Improved texture, tone, and firmness with no downtime</p>
</section>

